---
title: Ssamjang Pork Lettuce Cups with Sweetcorn Fried Rice
description: Crunchy and green, lettuce cups are a fun way to involve a bit of veg into dinner. Their job is to hold all the ssamjang pork and
veggies together. Doll out a helping of charred corn fried rice to the plate and this is one fun dinner that we can’t get enough of.

